law.text:
In addition to the information required under Subtitle 1 of this title, each application for a license shall include:
The type of dealership applied for;
If the application is made for a partnership, the name and address of each partner applying for the partnership;
If the application is made for a corporation or for a partnership by a corporate partner, the name and address of each of the officers applying for the corporation or partnership;
If the application is made for a corporation, the place of its incorporation; and
The nature of the business to be conducted at each address.
